title: $3200-2/1 Ft Lauderdale Bungalow-Stylishly Furnished-Fenced Yard
neighborhood: Ft Lauderdale-Between Las Olas and 17th St-Tarpon River
posting_body: ["It doesn't get any cuter than this adorable bungalow with a spacious yard in close-in and convenient to downtown Croissant Park.", 'Two bedrooms and one stylish bath plus two comfortable bedrooms compliment the chic open space living room / dining room / kitchen space in this stylish abode.', 'Available for annual lease, it comes fully furnished but can be unfurnished for the right tenant.', 'With quick access to Davie Blvd and beyond, this great rental as home base offers a quick trip to Whole Foods and the entire 17th ST Causeway area, the airport, I-95 to Miami or West Palm and an easy jaunt to the beach.', 'Water/Sewer and Lawn Maintenance included in rent.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE – NOT SHORT TERM.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
